Had a goob time visiting @urgentvetfrisco!❤️ As some of my frens may know, about a month ago I had an allergic reaction very late at night to my rabies vaccine and it sent my spare hooman into panic mode to find an urgent care or emergency vet at almost 11:00 PM. Even though my vaccine was given in the morning and I was given a shot to help with my allergic reaction (this wasn't my first rodeo, fren), my face was very swollen and I clearly did not look normal. 

Luckily, the hooman found an UrgentVet in our area and we rushed on over. We got there 10 min. before closing and the nice hoomans there greeted us at the door and were very calm and friendly - head pats were given. They took care of me very quickly and even called my hooman to check up on me the next day. 

12/10 experience at UrgentVet. Highly recommend my pet parent friends to know ur pet urgent care facilities in ur area in case of an emergency and if ur near an @urgentvetclinics, make them ur place!🩺
